# S4.3 Handover Log — CI 强化
# Date: 2026-05-27
# Task: Sprint 4.3 — CI coverage gate + NATS/CH/Redis services
# Status: COMPLETED

## Changes Summary

### Modified Files

1. **.github/workflows/ci.yml** — 新增 coverage gate (≥60%)
   - backend-test job 原有 Coverage summary 步骤仅打印覆盖率
   - 新增 Coverage gate 步骤：覆盖率 < 60% 时 `exit 1` 阻塞 PR merge
   - 使用 `go tool cover -func=coverage.out | tail -1` 提取总覆盖率
   - THRESHOLD=60 (P2-1 要求的最低门控值)

2. **.github/workflows/ci-nightly.yml** — 新增 NATS/CH/Redis 服务
   - nightly-test job 新增 3 个 service container:
     - redis:8-alpine (health check: redis-cli ping)
     - clickhouse/clickhouse-server:24 (health check: SELECT 1)
     - nats:2.10-alpine (health check: nats server check connection)
   - go test env 新增: REDIS_HOST/PORT, CH_HOST/PORT/USER/PASSWORD/DATABASE, NATS_URL
   - nightly-data-check job 新增 CH + NATS service containers + env vars
   - Coverage summary 升级为 warning-level gate (不阻塞 nightly，但发 warning)

### 已存在的安全扫描 (P2-2 已满足)
- security-scan.yml: gosec (severity medium) + trivy fs (HIGH,CRITICAL) + trivy image
- dependabot.yml: gomod, npm, docker (weekly, Asia/Shanghai)
- ci.yml verify-cards-strict job: detect-all (R0 五件套) + verify-cards-strict MILESTONE=M11

### CI Pipeline 全景

| Job | 触发 | 服务 | 门控 |
|-----|------|------|------|
| line-limits | push/PR | — | Python check-file-lines |
| backend-lint | push/PR | — | go vet + golangci-lint |
| backend-test | push/PR | PG | -short + coverage ≥60% |
| proto-breaking | push/PR | — | buf breaking |
| proto-drift | push/PR | — | buf generate diff |
| migration-down | push/PR | — | .up ↔ .down 配对 |
| frontend | push/PR | — | eslint + build |
| verify-cards | push/PR | — | detect-all + M11 verify |
| security-scan | push/PR/cron | — | gosec + trivy |
| nightly-test | cron 02:37 | PG+Redis+CH+NATS | full test + coverage warning |
| nightly-data | cron 02:37 | CH+NATS | md-doctor + slo-report |

